data.description: This meticulously maintained and beautifully updated home, nestled on a little over half acre adorned with stunning live oak trees in a quiet neighborhood, offers the perfect blend of tranquility and convenience. Easily within walking distance to downtown Bulverde makes it an excellent choice for both first-time homebuyers seeking a starter home and empty nesters looking for a peaceful retreat. Seller is retired; she has a large watchdog and a day-sleeper son living with her that both require relocation for Showings and kindly asks that Agents schedule between 10am-7pm with 2-hour notice.
